{"id":1266,"date":"2024-08-04T16:25:28","date_gmt":"2024-08-04T16:25:28","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/?post_type=wiki&#038;p=1266"},"modified":"2024-08-04T16:25:28","modified_gmt":"2024-08-04T16:25:28","slug":"mission-068","status":"publish","type":"wiki","link":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/missions\/mission-068\/","title":{"rendered":"Mission #068: The Most Dangerous Game"},"content":{"rendered":"<table class=\"table left grey\">\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th colspan=\"2\"class=\"text-large center\">Mission #068: The Most Dangerous Game<\/th>\n<\/tr>\n<\/thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<th>Start Location<\/th>\n<td>Magnolia Fields, Northwest Grove &#8211; man with spiky hair<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Unlock Requirements<\/th>\n<td>\n<ul>\n<li>Completed main story missions up until Magnolia Town<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Objectives<\/th>\n<td>Capture 25 Pokemon in one Safari Zone game on any difficulty<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Reward<\/th>\n<td><u>Item<\/u>: <strong>30 Beast Balls<\/strong><\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<\/tbody>\n<\/table>\n<p>A man in the northeast Magnolia Fields grove wants you to catch as many Safari Zone Pokemon as possible in one session &#8211; at least 25. If you manage this, you\u2019ll get 30 Beast Balls.<\/p>\n<h2>Starting the Mission<\/h2>\n<p>There\u2019s a secluded grove of trees and wild grass in the northwest part of Magnolia Fields, behind some Cut trees.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/068\/01-pokemon-unbound-the-man-in-the-grove.jpg\" alt=\"The man in the grove \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>The man in the grove<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>Speak to the man there and he\u2019ll give you a mission to catch at least 25 Pok\u00e9mon in one session in the Safari Zone.<\/p>\n<h2>How to Complete<\/h2>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/068\/02-pokemon-unbound-the-safari-zone-gate.jpg\" alt=\"The Safari Zone gate \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>The Safari Zone gate<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>The Safari Zone is a minigame in Pok\u00e9mon Unbound, not an actual location. And it can be accessed through the east gate of Polder Town.<\/p>\n<p>You get 30 Safari Balls per session, which means you can at maximum catch up to 30 Pok\u00e9mon each time.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/068\/03-pokemon-unbound-catching-a-pokemon-in-the-safari-zone.jpg\" alt=\"Catching a Pokemon in the Safari Zone \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Catching a Pokemon in the Safari Zone<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>This means that in order for your mission to catch 25 in one session to succeed, you can\u2019t miss a Pok\u00e9mon with a catching throw more than five times.<\/p>\n<p>It\u2019s hard to do, but if you succeed, you\u2019ll get 30 Beast Balls.<\/p>\n<div class=\"callout-box\">\n<strong>Tip:<\/strong> Beast Balls are useful for catching Ultra Beasts, which are a lot of the Pok\u00e9mon that come out of Hoopa\u2019s portals during Mission #050: Portal Purge. If you\u2019re doing that mission, they will come in handy.\n<\/div>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/068\/04-pokemon-unbound-another-source-of-beast-balls-at-cube-corp.jpg\" alt=\"Another source of Beast Balls, at Cube Corp \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Another source of Beast Balls, at Cube Corp<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n        <a href=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/missions\/\" class=\"parent-page-card\">\n            <picture class=\"card-img\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"200\" height=\"200\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/07\/missions-icon.jpg\" class=\"attachment-full size-full wp-post-image\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/07\/missions-icon.jpg 200w, https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/07\/missions-icon-150x150.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 200px) 100vw, 200px\" \/>\t\t\t\t            <\/picture>\n            <span class=\"card-info\">\n                <span class=\"card-info__caption\">Back to:<\/span>\n                <strong class=\"wiki-title\">All Missions<\/strong>\n            <\/span>\n        <\/a>\n\n\t\t\n","protected":false},"featured_media":1267,"parent":282,"menu_order":2,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"_acf_changed":false},"categories":[11],"class_list":["post-1266","wiki","type-wiki","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-missions"],"acf":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/wiki\/1266","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/wiki"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/wiki"}],"up":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/wiki\/282"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/1267"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=1266"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=1266"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}